{"tid":1532461,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解好似冇人提大班冰皮月餅撐香港之路被中國封殺？","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:55:26.000Z","uid":26836,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d06038708c4fd25ab3a39315ec306944cc3aa81e","tid":1532461,"uid":26836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=3_60002505&amp;i=20190902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D3_60002505%26i%3D20190902&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1asIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=ea938c23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D3_60002505%26i%3D20190902&h=17d1eda8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=3_60002505&amp;i=20190902</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n「大班冰皮月餅，始終係主角。」這句廣告對白大家應該很熟悉，但大班應該萬萬沒想到今年竟成為白色恐怖的主角。<br />\n<br />\n話說早前大班麵包西餅的太子爺郭勇維（Garic），在社交平台轉載了兩張圖片，關於香港之路以及諷刺藍絲的圖片，結果被中國網民截圖，並在中國各社交平台上瘋傳，最後被官媒《人民日報》、《環球網》齊齊加入篤灰行動，指郭勇維支持亂港分子，因此引發封殺行動，再次在香港掀起商界白色恐怖！<br />\n<br />\n雖然郭勇維隨即於個人社交平台道歉，指個人分享與大班麵包西餅立場無關，但似乎無法平息大陸封殺行動，大班於天貓及京東網購平台已被消失下架。<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖蔓延，有香港網民發起今年要「All in 大班月餅」，呼籲香港人撐香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者到大班餅店實地考察，依記者所見沒有發現人流有很大影響，跟店員交談過，店員指生意很不錯：「很多人來買，尤其剛才有兩位女士，在雪櫃拿了一堆，十幾盒左右。」<br />\n同場記者又與顧客交談，有顧客表示害怕帶回深圳時被扣留，但最終還是有購買，只是不會帶內中國。而另一位顧客則指這不是他考慮範圍：「支持學生？沒有所謂的，各有各政見，我們購物都是看品質。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實無論白色恐怖有多恐怖，我們需要恐懼的是恐懼本身，多支持本土企業，才能把本土品牌發揚光大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n【撐學生】<br />\n召集有心人 撐學生全年睇《蘋果》<br />\n立即按此<br />\n<br />\n今年中秋唔洗買咩美心月餅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">買大班！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n分店地址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taipan.com.hk/location.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taipan.com.hk%2Flocation.html&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1asIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=ff65dfda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.taipan.com.hk/location.html</a>"},{"pid":"4fddf24bde1623bb4e4e5ae6d202f91906a3d6da","tid":1532461,"uid":26836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a2d6fd4498b881426a45d36508d3374a1fc67312","tid":1532461,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90272e863313c96c55994e19668c4b1a99d0ff8","tid":1532461,"uid":277187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"今日喺Aeon目測所有月餅檔最好生意就係大班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38de6f53c1fadd97c69913c57f094f6965415d7","tid":1532461,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"大班，你年年啲廣告好撚煩膠，改改佢"},{"pid":"f651a6dfeb5b1368154b0ffab981c5ed66682486","tid":1532461,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"支持 其實細個覺得大班係好貴 <br />\n希望之後可以走d 中青年線既包裝同形象"},{"pid":"cfd7c973aa8c50af55c52357f8e6507cd56cfba3","tid":1532461,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"有個幾兩個星期先係中秋, 其間可以發生好多事, 跟車太貼小心炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議大家等到下星期一後, 睇下淘寶天貓重揾唔揾到大班先再決定幫唔幫, 就算想即刻幫暫時都唔好太大手入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}